WEBVTT

00:00:58.588 --> 00:01:00.609
Ai mund te shumezoje dy numra treshifore

00:01:00.609 --> 00:01:02.396
shume lehte me mendje,

00:01:02.396 --> 00:01:06.154
nderkohe kur bie fjala 
per te bere nje bisede,

00:01:06.154 --> 00:01:08.215
ai ka veshtiresi te medha.

00:01:08.215 --> 00:01:10.274
Ai nuk vendos kontakt me sy.

00:01:10.274 --> 00:01:12.397
Ai ka veshtiresi ne fillimin e nje bisede,

00:01:12.397 --> 00:01:14.132
ndjehet cuditshem,

00:01:14.132 --> 00:01:15.950
dhe kur nervozohet,

00:01:15.950 --> 00:01:17.675
ai mbyllet ne vetvete.

00:01:17.675 --> 00:01:19.157
Por nderkohe te dy keta djem

00:01:19.157 --> 00:01:23.341
kane te njejten diagnoze te crregullimit
te spektrit te autizmit.

00:01:23.341 --> 00:01:25.769
Nje prej gjerave qe na shqeteson

00:01:25.769 --> 00:01:27.366
eshte nese ka apo jo realisht

00:01:27.366 --> 00:01:29.339
nje epidemi autizmi.

00:01:29.339 --> 00:01:31.819
Keto dite, nje ne 88 femije